</section>

<!-- THE PROBLEM -->
<section class="lg9-section-soft">
  <div class="lg9-shell">
    <div class="lg9-grid-2" style="align-items:center;">
      <div>
        <p class="lg9-kicker">The Core Problem</p>
        <h2 class="lg9-title-md" style="margin:10px 0 14px;">Your Pool Deck Is Leaking Revenue Every Hour.</h2>
        <p class="lg9-copy">Every pool deck loses revenue the same three ways. Guests leave to charge phones. They skip food orders because no server is nearby. They cut their stay short because they do not trust leaving valuables on a lounge chair. Every hour a guest walks off the deck is a missed food and beverage opportunity. The LounGenie solves all three problems at the guest&#8217;s seat.</p>
        <div style="display:grid;gap:14px;margin-top:22px;">
          <div class="lg9-card" style="padding:18px 20px;">
            <strong style="display:block;margin-bottom:6px;">Guests leave to charge</strong>
            <span class="lg9-copy" style="font-size:15px;">A dead phone sends guests off the pool deck. Without charging at the seat, they leave — and often don&#8217;t come back.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="lg9-card" style="padding:18px 20px;">
            <strong style="display:block;margin-bottom:6px;">Orders get skipped</strong>
            <span class="lg9-copy" style="font-size:15px;">When no server is nearby and there&#8217;s no easy way to order, guests settle for less and your food and beverage revenue drops.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="lg9-card" style="padding:18px 20px;">
            <strong style="display:block;margin-bottom:6px;">Valuables send guests home early</strong>
            <span class="lg9-copy" style="font-size:15px;">Guests who don&#8217;t trust leaving their phone and wallet on a lounge chair cut their visit short. Every early departure is lost spend.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lg9-media" style="aspect-ratio:16/12;"><!-- wp:image {"id":8769,"sizeSlug":"large","linkDestination":"none"} -->
<!-- /wp:image --></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

